			<div class="content" id="post-content-2050616">
									

<p>My apologies for the necro-post, but I'm currently looking back through the 001 proposals and saw that someone had commented on my post from long ago. I had deleted the above account (of a different name) out of frustration with this site for reasons long-since buried, but, out of human curiosity, could not stay away for long. If you ever see this post, I find it interesting that you would recognize this as possibly your own writing, and find an odd satisfaction in someone mistaking it for their own.</p>
